          {
            "time": "2:12",
            "timeSeconds": 132,
            "text": "I'm not feeling well."
          },
          {
            "time": "2:13",
            "timeSeconds": 133,
            "text": "I need to sit down."
          },
          {
            "time": "2:14",
            "timeSeconds": 134,
            "text": "Sit down."
          },
          {
            "time": "2:15",
            "timeSeconds": 135,
            "text": "Hey, Stanley."
          },
          {
            "time": "2:16",
            "timeSeconds": 136,
            "text": "Stanley."
          },
          {
            "time": "2:17",
            "timeSeconds": 137,
            "text": "Are you okay?"
          },
          {
            "time": "2:18",
            "timeSeconds": 138,
            "text": "Help!"
          },
          {
            "time": "2:19",
            "timeSeconds": 139,
            "text": "Oh, my God!"
          },
          {
            "time": "2:20",
            "timeSeconds": 140,
            "text": "Dwight!"
          },
          {
            "time": "2:21",
            "timeSeconds": 141,
            "text": "Get out of here."
          },
          {
            "time": "2:22",
            "timeSeconds": 142,
            "text": "Dwight!"
          },
          {
            "time": "2:23",
            "timeSeconds": 143,
            "text": "Oh, my God."
          },
          {
            "time": "2:24",
            "timeSeconds": 144,
            "text": "Can you tell me why you had to go?"
          },
          {
            "time": "2:27",
            "timeSeconds": 147,
            "text": "Dwight, you had to cut the face off the dummy."
          },
          {
            "time": "2:29",
            "timeSeconds": 149,
            "text": "I didn't think it was very realistic in the movie,"
          },
          {
            "time": "2:32",
            "timeSeconds": 152,
            "text": "and it turns out it's pretty realistic."
          },
          {
            "time": "2:34",
            "timeSeconds": 154,
            "text": "We had to pay for it."
          },
          {
            "time": "2:35",
            "timeSeconds": 155,
            "text": "It cost us $3,500."
          },
          {
            "time": "2:37",
            "timeSeconds": 157,
            "text": "$5,300 for a dummy?"
          },
          {
            "time": "2:39",
            "timeSeconds": 159,
            "text": "Wow."
          },
          {
            "time": "2:41",
            "timeSeconds": 161,
            "text": "Okay, look, David, this is why we have training."
          },
          {
            "time": "2:46",
            "timeSeconds": 166,
            "text": "We start with the dummy, and we learn from our mistakes,"
          },
          {
            "time": "2:49",
            "timeSeconds": 169,
            "text": "and now Dwight knows not to cut the face off a real person."
          },
          {
            "time": "2:57",
            "timeSeconds": 177,
            "text": "Thanks for watching!"
          }
        ],
        "hasSubtitles": true
      }
    ]
  }
]